    See <a href="/guides/tomato-grafting-clips-vs-silicone-clips/">tomato grafting clips vs silicone clips</a> and <a href="/guides/2-0-to-4-5-mm-grafting-clips-for-home-gardeners/">2.0 to 4.5 mm grafting clips for home gardeners</a>.
